<item>
            <title>[LU-13048] Non-blocking migrate: Unable to release file from disk (Cannot send HSM request)</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13048</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The same root-case like in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5896&quot; title=&quot;lfs: can&amp;#39;t release a migrated file&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-5896&quot;&gt;LU-5896&lt;/a&gt;, but about non-blocking migrate.&lt;br/&gt;
Non blocking swap layout (lfs migrate -n) uses different request and need separate fix.&lt;br/&gt;
old and new object version need to be added to struct close_data.&lt;br/&gt;
To reproduce add -n to migrate operation in sanity-ham 607&lt;br/&gt;
